Package: MoreColours
Type: Package
Title: Curated Color Palettes for Data Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Massie", email = "thomas.massie@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of carefully selected color palettes for data visualization,
    including categorical and sequential palettes. Designed for accessibility and
    visual appeal in scientific and business graphics.
